'''Danevirke Museum''' is a museum located a few kilometers just outside the city of [[Schleswig, Schleswig-Holstein]], and the text inside the museum is written in both Danish and German. It opened in 1990 and focuses on the history of [[Dannewerk]] from the Viking Age to the present.

